#: ../../agent_skills.rst:557
msgid "Memory 语义"
msgstr "Memory Semantics"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:559
msgid "``PersonAgent`` 中有两类容易混淆的记忆："
msgstr "There are two types of memory in ``PersonAgent`` that are easily confused:"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:561
msgid "``AGENT_MEMORY.md`` 是运行时维护的会话摘要，保存当前任务、已完成动作和错误等信息，主要服务长线程压缩与恢复。"
msgstr ""
"``AGENT_MEMORY.md`` is a runtime-maintained session summary that stores "
"current tasks, completed actions, and errors, primarily serving long "
"thread compression and recovery."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:562
msgid ""
"``state/memory.jsonl`` 是 ``memory`` 技能维护的经验记忆，保存人物在仿真中值得跨 tick "
"检索的事件、关系、地点、承诺和计划结果。"
msgstr ""
"``state/memory.jsonl`` is the experiential memory maintained by the "
"``memory`` skill, storing events, relationships, locations, commitments, "
"and plan outcomes from the simulation that are worth cross-tick "
"retrieval."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:564
msgid ""
"``memory`` 技能不是每步固定执行的收尾层。是否写入 "
"``state/memory.jsonl``，由工具循环根据当前事件是否值得保留来决定。这样可以减少重复记忆，也让长期记忆更像“重要经验”而不是完整日志。"
msgstr ""
"The ``memory`` skill is not a fixed finalization layer executed every "
"step. Whether to write to ``state/memory.jsonl`` is determined by the "
"tool loop based on whether the current event is worth retaining. This "
"reduces duplicate memories and makes long-term memory more like "
"\"important experiences\" rather than a complete log."

