msgstr "``POST /reload``: Hot-reloads a single skill"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:580
msgid "``POST /remove``：删除自定义技能"
msgstr "``POST /remove``: Deletes a custom skill"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:581
#, python-brace-format
msgid "``GET /{name}/info``：查看技能详细信息（含 SKILL.md 内容）"
msgstr ""
"``GET /{name}/info``: Views detailed skill information (including "
"SKILL.md content)"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:583
msgid "这些接口同时被 VS Code 扩展与手动调试流程使用。"
msgstr ""
"These endpoints are used by both the VS Code extension and manual "
"debugging workflows."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:587
msgid "自定义 Skill 最小示例"
msgstr "Minimal Custom Skill Example"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:589
msgid "目录："
msgstr "Directory:"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:598
msgid "``SKILL.md``："
msgstr "``SKILL.md``:"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:611
msgid "``scripts/hello_skill.py``："
msgstr "``scripts/hello_skill.py``:"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:632
msgid "导入并启用后，主 LLM 会在合适上下文中选择它执行。"
msgstr ""
"After importing and enabling, the main LLM will select it for execution "
"in an appropriate context."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:636
msgid "最佳实践"
msgstr "Best Practices"

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:638
msgid "``description`` 写成\"触发条件 + 输出结果\"，便于模型选择器判断。"
msgstr ""
"Write ``description`` as \"trigger condition + output result\" to help "
"the model selector make decisions."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:639
msgid "若依赖其它 skill，在正文写清并引导先 ``activate_skill``。"
msgstr ""
"If the skill depends on other skills, state this clearly in the body and "
"guide the model to ``activate_skill`` first."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:640
msgid "Skill 代码尽量幂等，避免重复执行造成状态污染。"
msgstr ""
"Keep skill code idempotent to avoid state pollution from repeated "
"execution."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:641
msgid "对关键技能保留清晰日志，便于复盘每步选择与执行。"
msgstr ""
"Maintain clear logs for critical skills to facilitate reviewing each "
"step's selection and execution."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:642
msgid "优先使用 Prompt-only 模式，只在需要确定性计算时才用 Subprocess script。"
msgstr ""
"Prefer the Prompt-only mode; use Subprocess script only when "
"deterministic computation is needed."

#: ../../agent_skills.rst:643
msgid "脚本中通过 ``--args-json`` 接收参数，输出以 JSON 打印到 stdout，产物写入 ``AGENT_WORK_DIR``。"
msgstr ""
"In scripts, receive parameters via ``--args-json``, print output as JSON "
"to stdout, and write artifacts to ``AGENT_WORK_DIR``."

